0.3.0
=====

* if a parameter in query arg (which could be a body) match a
  url substitution, use it and remove it from query (or body)

0.2.0
=====

* DELETE is not GET-like - it is POST-like and accepts a body

0.1.6
=====

* fix POST or PUT (body, cb) call - empty query in that case

0.1.5
=====

* cb(status, responseText) fixing previous version

0.1.4
=====

* cb(status, body) instead of just cb(status) on errors

0.1.3
=====

* fix and explain signatures

0.1.2
=====

* allow calls without callback

0.1.1
=====

* fix a bug with cross-domain requests and custom X-Requested-With
  HTTP header: it initiates a preflighted request.
